00:00:58.240 --> 00:01:01.080
[Music]

00:01:01.080 --> 00:01:03.700
We want to melt all of our
chocolate in a double boiler.

00:01:03.700 --> 00:01:05.140
That's when you take one pan,

00:01:05.140 --> 00:01:07.340
and put it in another pan
that's full of water.

00:01:07.340 --> 00:01:08.760
This prevents the pan
with the chocolate

00:01:08.770 --> 00:01:10.840
