00:01:32.640 --> 00:01:35.260
Stir that in until you have
a uniform consistency.

00:01:35.260 --> 00:01:37.480
It won't be as smooth as it was before.

00:01:37.480 --> 00:01:45.740
[Music]

00:01:45.740 --> 00:01:47.660
Once the sugar and
hot cocoa are mixed in,

00:01:47.670 --> 00:01:48.670
