00:02:10.020 --> 00:02:19.460
[Music]

00:02:19.460 --> 00:02:23.340
At this point, what we have
is a deliciously rich, extremely

00:02:23.340 --> 00:02:26.380
chocolatey mixture that's
frankly a little too strong.

00:02:26.380 --> 00:02:28.480
You wouldn't want to eat this plain,

00:02:28.480 --> 00:02:30.880
