00:02:33.980 --> 00:02:35.280
So what we actually
need to do now

00:02:35.280 --> 00:02:37.700
is water it down with water.

00:02:37.700 --> 00:02:40.500
Let's add 1 and 1/2 cups
of water into our mixture.

00:02:40.500 --> 00:02:46.000
